con:testCase.name: Local Print - Attachments
con:testCase.con:description:
Exercises Local Print batching using the Attachments response type.
REQUIRED PROPERTIES: * Inputfile - the filename of the extract data. Specify ONLY the filename and extension. * Note: the file should be physically located in "inputs" directory. This directory should be * in the same directory as the soapUI project file.
USAGE: Run the test case using the "play" button above. Review Custom Properties to see returned results as properties, or look at the DoRequest item to see actual response.

con:config.script:
/* * Perform any routines after the request. */
// Get a reference to the Common test case and run the step. testCase = testRunner.getTestCase().getTestSuite().getProject().getTestSuiteByName("TestBed").getTestCaseByName("Common") initStep = testCase.testSteps["ParseResultsAttachments"] initStep.run(testRunner, context)
